Package edu.biu.scapi.circuits.garbledCircuit

Interface Summary
GarbledBooleanCircuit GarbledBooleanCircuit is a general interface for all basic garbled circuits.
GarbledBooleanCircuitExtended This interface is an extension for the basic garbled boolean circuit, GarbledBooleanCircuit.
GarbledGate An interface that StandardGarbledGate's and any specialized or optimized garbled gate will implement.
GarbledTablesHolder This is a general interface for garbled tables holder.
GarblingParameters A general interface for a circuits' garbling parameters.
 

Class Summary
CircuitCreationValues A class that hold the values used to create the circuit.
ExtendedGarbledTablesHolder This class holds the garbled tables of the extended garbled circuit, it contains the garbled tables of the inner garbled circuit along with garbled tables of the input identity gates and output identity gates.
FreeXORGarblingParameters This is the garbling parameters' class for a Free XOR circuit.
GarbledBooleanCircuitExtendedImp This class is an implementation of an extended garbled boolean circuit.
GarbledBooleanCircuitImp A concrete implementation of GarbledBooleanCircuit that is common for all types of circuits.
GarbledWire This class is a software representation of a garbled Wire.
IdentityGate The identity gates are used in the extended circuit.
MinimizeAESSetKeyGarblingParameters This is the garbling parameters' class for MinimizeAESSetKey circuit.
StandardGarblingParameters This is the garbling parameters' class for Standard circuit.
